{"tid":96140,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"精神病紀錄揮手區","createTime":"2017-01-26T14:41:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T17:04:19.000Z","uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"965fe7d636e7ed23094f440362b31bc8cfe487ab","tid":96140,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:41:22.000Z","msg":"我是被逼的<br />\n無啦啦俾新生會安泰軒個pk社工捉返去尖沙咀<br />\n然後俾尖沙咀踢我返青山睇醫生<br />\n<br />\n從此被冠上精神病紀錄<br />\n<br />\n病歷寫上paranoid schizophrenia (最新狀況係episodic remittent)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f0feeef42d862991ea3ad74115d7f58a10433ad","tid":96140,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:44:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我是被逼的<br />\n無啦啦俾新生會安泰軒個pk社工捉返去尖沙咀<br />\n然後俾尖沙咀踢我返青山睇醫生<br />\n<br />\n從此被冠上精神病紀錄<br />\n<br />\n病歷寫上paranoid schizophrenia (最新狀況係episodic remittent)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />四眼短髮男社工？？"},{"pid":"89efd647b7b697c3eea1a8829a26344f0a1a5314","tid":96140,"uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:44:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我是被逼的<br />\n無啦啦俾新生會安泰軒個pk社工捉返去尖沙咀<br />\n然後俾尖沙咀踢我返青山睇醫生<br />\n<br />\n從此被冠上精神病紀錄<br />\n<br />\n病歷寫上paranoid schizophrenia (最新狀況係episodic remittent)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />四眼短髮男社工？？</blockquote><br />\n唔係<br />\n社工女人黎嫁<br />\n最後一次佢上年6月打黎 我CUT左線<br />\n從此冇再見佢<br />\n反正我都唔會同佢講真話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a41854e37a44bea123e9336830619de1815e805","tid":96140,"uid":60848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:49:18.000Z","msg":"你講左咩比佢聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead5f7e4eb27f8cf458a30a0881bdbd993bd8c99","tid":96140,"uid":22358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:50:32.000Z","msg":"精神科護士留名"},{"pid":"9de7181b83c33ef4b88dddec09aa6c96d28821b8","tid":96140,"uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:50:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你講左咩比佢聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果我唔同佢講<br />\n就唔會搞成咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7af6f606086042d446a8b9947e22a4609aa2579f","tid":96140,"uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:51:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>精神科護士留名</blockquote><br />\n精神科護士 好高人工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a9b3839c024dd94278040eff7426a7336dc6d6","tid":96140,"uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:51:58.000Z","msg":"我覺得醫生少少事就屈人痴線<br />\n<br />\n明明我只不過係諗唔開 唔開心<br />\n<br />\n佢就然咁就話我有思覺失調<br />\n<br />\n真係亂斷症 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b19de9d7f7c8ac9d0608846178971dd6b291fdd","tid":96140,"uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:55:08.000Z","msg":"我唔識講咁多年裡面的感覺<br />\n<br />\n只可以話情緒精神最差最亂既時候<br />\n<br />\n出去食野係只會食白飯<br />\n<br />\n唔想夾送<br />\n<br />\n唔敢亂郁<br />\n<br />\n一郁 周圍真實存在的聲音會放大更多倍 鑽入我的思維 我好驚<br />\n<br />\n覺得自己只配食白飯<br />\n<br />\n屋企叫我食肉同菜<br />\n<br />\n我都唔想理佢地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edbfe50fcd7064e111148d32d30f8edac20bd3c6","tid":96140,"uid":22358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:57:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔識講咁多年裡面的感覺<br />\n<br />\n只可以話情緒精神最差最亂既時候<br />\n<br />\n出去食野係只會食白飯<br />\n<br />\n唔想夾送<br />\n<br />\n唔敢亂郁<br />\n<br />\n一郁 周圍真實存在的聲音會放大更多倍 鑽入我的思維 我好驚<br />\n<br />\n覺得自己只配食白飯<br />\n<br />\n屋企叫我食肉同菜<br />\n<br />\n我都唔想理佢地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會咁諗？<br />\n點解無自信覺得自己無價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6257b4639592cb0114bf8f9dc1cb5418d05bd343","tid":96140,"uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:58:42.000Z","msg":"抗精神分裂藥物同抗抑鬱藥物藥理上的唔同<br />\n食完之後因應我身體反應<br />\n又會令我的精神情緒狀況有好大差異結果<br />\n<br />\n兩年前第一次食amisulpride之類的anti psychotics<br />\n心裡面咩感覺都冇晒<br />\n連打機都冇絲毫興奮感覺<br />\n冇晒任何motivation<br />\n全日就係訓上床度唔知做乜<br />\n<br />\n都唔知點解老母咁鍾意叫醒我<br />\n明知我食左藥<br />\n而我起身真係咩都唔想做<br />\n連機都冇MOOD打<br />\n<br />\n由於心理治療同埋藥物開始有效<br />\n我的奇怪感覺同聲波之類 開始慢慢退散<br />\n<br />\n但係取而代之的係無盡空虛<br />\n咩感覺都冇晒<br />\n咩都唔想做<br />\n淨係想訓<br />\n<br />\n果陣唯一有的想法係:<br />\n可能死左都只不過係咁樣的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4a9a75b816b8e857a8590e87c0c0e82c1e57ac","tid":96140,"uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:59:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我唔識講咁多年裡面的感覺<br />\n<br />\n只可以話情緒精神最差最亂既時候<br />\n<br />\n出去食野係只會食白飯<br />\n<br />\n唔想夾送<br />\n<br />\n唔敢亂郁<br />\n<br />\n一郁 周圍真實存在的聲音會放大更多倍 鑽入我的思維 我好驚<br />\n<br />\n覺得自己只配食白飯<br />\n<br />\n屋企叫我食肉同菜<br />\n<br />\n我都唔想理佢地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會咁諗？<br />\n點解無自信覺得自己無價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣野我13歲升F2左右開始就係咁<br />\n<br />\n其實冇咩特別理由<br />\n<br />\n人一到青春期由於腦生理亂晒<br />\n<br />\n就會開始亂諗野同埋情緒化..."},{"pid":"6ef96f4ff2d3172e6158a1f2874b6dbb36444fed","tid":96140,"uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:00:53.000Z","msg":"我因為某一年個人太情緒化太痴線得罪好多人<br />\n<br />\n於是之後一年我覺得自己做錯好多事 對唔住全世界 之類"},{"pid":"a117e6bb00be585c73988fec4786dafb01d5f6cd","tid":96140,"uid":22358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:02:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我唔識講咁多年裡面的感覺<br />\n<br />\n只可以話情緒精神最差最亂既時候<br />\n<br />\n出去食野係只會食白飯<br />\n<br />\n唔想夾送<br />\n<br />\n唔敢亂郁<br />\n<br />\n一郁 周圍真實存在的聲音會放大更多倍 鑽入我的思維 我好驚<br />\n<br />\n覺得自己只配食白飯<br />\n<br />\n屋企叫我食肉同菜<br />\n<br />\n我都唔想理佢地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會咁諗？<br />\n點解無自信覺得自己無價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣野我13歲升F2左右開始就係咁<br />\n<br />\n其實冇咩特別理由<br />\n<br />\n人一到青春期由於腦生理亂晒<br />\n<br />\n就會開始亂諗野同埋情緒化...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屋企/上三代有無精神病既家族史？"},{"pid":"c0a60dc6f078233291736c33c35677e10a3d1e34","tid":96140,"uid":62464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:03:00.000Z","msg":"抑鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得自己多重人格"},{"pid":"dd0d9e9e487f6698936352415aeccec4a1692e82","tid":96140,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:03:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我唔識講咁多年裡面的感覺<br />\n<br />\n只可以話情緒精神最差最亂既時候<br />\n<br />\n出去食野係只會食白飯<br />\n<br />\n唔想夾送<br />\n<br />\n唔敢亂郁<br />\n<br />\n一郁 周圍真實存在的聲音會放大更多倍 鑽入我的思維 我好驚<br />\n<br />\n覺得自己只配食白飯<br />\n<br />\n屋企叫我食肉同菜<br />\n<br />\n我都唔想理佢地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會咁諗？<br />\n點解無自信覺得自己無價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣野我13歲升F2左右開始就係咁<br />\n<br />\n其實冇咩特別理由<br />\n<br />\n人一到青春期由於腦生理亂晒<br />\n<br />\n就會開始亂諗野同埋情緒化...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屋企/上三代有無精神病既家族史？</blockquote><br />\n冇 真係冇"},{"pid":"57de48571231a82eb18f1ad6233d07b0efe4211a","tid":96140,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:03:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抑鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得自己多重人格</blockquote><br />\n怎麼多重人格法"},{"pid":"c92e6870238485b81b184c55c39c6e0e1e74c897","tid":96140,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:04:58.000Z","msg":"從此走上被精神分裂的不歸路<br />\n<br />\n而我覺得我只不過是少許情緒困擾<br />\n<br />\n並不至於psychosis程度<br />\n<br />\n但竟被一私家醫生診斷為思覺失調<br />\n<br />\n然後青山醫生因此先入為主認為我真的有精神分裂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d26f9a14ee85cb3b912dcb8bdb2706d1a434db","tid":96140,"uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:06:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我唔識講咁多年裡面的感覺<br />\n<br />\n只可以話情緒精神最差最亂既時候<br />\n<br />\n出去食野係只會食白飯<br />\n<br />\n唔想夾送<br />\n<br />\n唔敢亂郁<br />\n<br />\n一郁 周圍真實存在的聲音會放大更多倍 鑽入我的思維 我好驚<br />\n<br />\n覺得自己只配食白飯<br />\n<br />\n屋企叫我食肉同菜<br />\n<br />\n我都唔想理佢地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會咁諗？<br />\n點解無自信覺得自己無價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣野我13歲升F2左右開始就係咁<br />\n<br />\n其實冇咩特別理由<br />\n<br />\n人一到青春期由於腦生理亂晒<br />\n<br />\n就會開始亂諗野同埋情緒化...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屋企/上三代有無精神病既家族史？</blockquote><br />\n冇 真係冇</blockquote><br />\n漏左講 當年仲未有咁嚴重 出現甚麼&quot;我不配食肉同菜&quot;係2015既事<br />\n我2015都成19 20歲了"},{"pid":"cf6b1865bd6cc8f3ebae244ba2b76a27215fb259","tid":96140,"uid":22358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:11:16.000Z","msg":"咁樓主依家仲有無穩定咁食精神科藥物？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73da0aad09fc5b79824e729d2403142a8285d65d","tid":96140,"uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:12:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁樓主依家仲有無穩定咁食精神科藥物？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇了 診都冇覆 醫生放過我話過多排再見"},{"pid":"64ee8cf18f6102152afbdc4aee4d4094df90b397","tid":96140,"uid":22358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:16:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁樓主依家仲有無穩定咁食精神科藥物？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇了 診都冇覆 醫生放過我話過多排再見</blockquote><br />\n咁你依家無食藥 有無話發覺多左psychotic symptom 或者情況差左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5992c330bf38f32ed616b3f98ce0fd76797bfe35","tid":96140,"uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:21:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁樓主依家仲有無穩定咁食精神科藥物？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇了 診都冇覆 醫生放過我話過多排再見</blockquote><br />\n咁你依家無食藥 有無話發覺多左psychotic symptom 或者情況差左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大幅度少過以前 有時仲有少少"},{"pid":"4da1bf02742e772c859773adf16e0a94628bcb89","tid":96140,"uid":62464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:25:01.000Z","msg":"介唔介意留tg傾？<br />\n總係覺得身邊冇咩人明白我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n@stupidpiggy"},{"pid":"97134ab522f1cc4d38c546988d3b418a3473e303","tid":96140,"uid":33310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:30:27.000Z","msg":"讀psycho留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}